{"id":14910,"date":"2026-03-06T08:00:05","date_gmt":"2026-03-06T13:00:05","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?p=14910"},"modified":"2026-03-05T09:14:34","modified_gmt":"2026-03-05T14:14:34","slug":"notre-diplomee-genevieve-dulude-de-celles-laureate-de-lours-dargent-a-berlin","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/nouvelle\/notre-diplomee-genevieve-dulude-de-celles-laureate-de-lours-dargent-a-berlin\/","title":{"rendered":"Notre dipl\u00f4m\u00e9e Genevi\u00e8ve Dulude-De Celles laur\u00e9ate de l\u2019Ours d\u2019Argent \u00e0 Berlin"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"chapeau\">Notre communaut\u00e9 s\u2019illustre \u00e0 l\u2019international\u2009! La cin\u00e9aste Genevi\u00e8ve Dulude-De Celles, dipl\u00f4m\u00e9e du programme <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/programmes\/cinema-et-communication\/\">Cin\u00e9ma et communication<\/a> du c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent, a remport\u00e9 l\u2019Ours d\u2019Argent du meilleur sc\u00e9nario lors de la 76<sup>e<\/sup> \u00e9dition du <a href=\"https:\/\/www.berlinale.de\/en\/home.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Festival international du film de Berlin<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>L\u2019Ours d\u2019Argent du meilleur sc\u00e9nario fait partie des huit remis lors de ce prestigieux festival. Le film de Genevi\u00e8ve Dulude-De Celles, <i>Nina Roza<\/i>, faisait partie des 22 \u0153uvres en comp\u00e9tition officielle.<\/p>\n<p>Le public qu\u00e9b\u00e9cois aura la chance de voir <i>Nina Roza\u00a0<\/i>dans les diff\u00e9rentes salles de la province \u00e0 partir du 24\u00a0avril prochain.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-14918 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NINA-ROZA_Affiche_FR-208x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"346\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NINA-ROZA_Affiche_FR-208x300.jpg 208w, https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NINA-ROZA_Affiche_FR-709x1024.jpg 709w, https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NINA-ROZA_Affiche_FR-768x1109.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/NINA-ROZA_Affiche_FR-scaled.jpg 1772w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 346px) 100vw, 346px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>F\u00e9licitations \u00e0 Genevi\u00e8ve et toute son \u00e9quipe pour cette distinction\u2009!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Notre communaut\u00e9 s\u2019illustre \u00e0 l\u2019international\u2009! La cin\u00e9aste Genevi\u00e8ve Dulude-De Celles, dipl\u00f4m\u00e9e du programme Cin\u00e9ma et communication du c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent, a remport\u00e9 l\u2019Ours d\u2019Argent du meilleur sc\u00e9nario lors de la 76e \u00e9dition du Festival international du film de Berlin. L\u2019Ours d\u2019Argent du meilleur sc\u00e9nario fait partie des huit remis lors de ce prestigieux festival. Le [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":14911,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[15],"sujet-actualite":[196,2611],"etiquette-interne":[2306,2337,2356],"class_list":["post-14910","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-nouvelle","sujet-actualite-honneurs","sujet-actualite-reussite-etudiante","etiquette-interne-cinema-et-communication","etiquette-interne-reussite-etudiante","etiquette-interne-attractivite"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_action":{"enabled":false,"date":"2026-05-04 22:14:42","action":"change-status","newStatus":"draft","terms":[],"taxonomy":"category"},"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14910","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl